{"tid":1677824,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[區選]  11月24日-孝子行動","createTime":"2019-10-27T10:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T14:22:08.000Z","uid":26336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2bf5206020f28c2307fe4c7433839527c1bd02","tid":1677824,"uid":26336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">區選-孝子行動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇番近年數據 每次區選唔計自動當選,紅區既地方 差唔多每區都係輸100-300票<br />\n參考資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uORZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c57cda0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">1.點解區選咁重要?</span></strong></span><br />\n拎資源呀屌你個閪, 對家比埋錢,比埋職能你都唔要?<br />\n好多時社區藍定黃取決於個區既地方工作 <br />\n有錢有資源 你都可以蛇齋餅粽,深圳一日遊,親子同樂電影日<br />\n同時要創造歷史 扭轉一直比共狗把持既區議會 比世界睇到&quot;民意&quot;到底係邊邊<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: gold;\">區議員不但可以直接選特首，更加是建制派的經濟命脈。目前區議員月薪為25,760元，另加約滿酬金15%，營運開支和雜項津貼每月共43,292元，一個區議員每年可動用開支約87.5萬元。以目前建制派民選加委任共399區議員計，一年的薪津就接近3億5千萬元。假設蛇齋餅粽的費用為每人500元,，這筆錢足以款待70萬選民，佔超過上屆區議會選舉投票人數120萬的一半。</span></em><br />\n一年三億咁樣比對家輕鬆羸? total 5年 15億 比你拎到 你想點蛇齋餅粽都得啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">2.喂 我未夠18歲 點幫到區選?</span></strong></span><br />\n好簡單 如果兩老都可以投非共陣營當然好<br />\n如果遊說失敗 仲可以點做?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做孝子</span></span><br />\n如果你經濟能力許可 緊係請老豆老媽子番大陸嘆番日 一千幾百 人地就少兩票,經濟能力唔許可既就搵下d團落力d sell下佢地 <br />\n除左老豆老母 大家好耐冇見既爺爺麻麻 <br />\n11月24日可以一早同佢地飲早茶 唔好比佢地上d不知名既旅遊巴<br />\n好多區只要100個人做到 已經羸左<br />\n以上只係例子之一 有咩方法做孝子乖孫大家可以自行發揮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">3.放低政治潔癖</span></strong></span><br />\n好多手足 聽到泛民+投票+錢 就會自動幫佢地上label ,血票,呃錢,為議席<br />\n其實呢個觀念同佢地見到暴力衝突一樣 都係會自帶潔癖<br />\n和非理都可以放低佢地既潔癖既時候 大家可唔可以都放低政治潔癖<br />\n係議會呢d實際層面上都可以做到 不分化 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n香港人咁多年黎 只要團結 每一樣野都係世一 <br />\n70年代 80年代 直到近代 由示威 鳩行 變到向世界輸出抗爭手法<br />\n比人warp起上埋wiki<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em><span style=\"color: teal;\">Tactics and methods surrounding the 2019 Hong Kong protests</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tactics_and_methods_surrounding_the_2019_Hong_Kong_protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTactics_and_methods_surrounding_the_2019_Hong_Kong_protests&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uORZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=92b8f52a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tactics_and_methods_surrounding_the_2019_Hong_Kong_protests</a></span><br />\n我地不分化 不割席 不篤灰 冇野係唔得!<br />\n唔好投白票,做孝子,拎番個15億<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Konger ,Stand as one</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 決一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9a2d48f13a645249d2434b9ee5b4b414649570ae","tid":1677824,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37d3f4c3a5dd1ea0d6a15e976546c1ba893a9a8","tid":1677824,"uid":26336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7fcb92908af57831fb0729a388a2077ecbc8e9d","tid":1677824,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"【重要】 對於 11.3 另一個維園集會有疑問？張文宣是唔是玩搞笑？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677803</a>"},{"pid":"6a6bf0f92bdaa85a6c9ac1d6ef258eb3a2842f58","tid":1677824,"uid":26336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f892803c6394d23e291abaec3c1be24ce5d792be","tid":1677824,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思講一講題外話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃大仙龍上手足請留意！</span><br />\n街站同呢個肥仔傾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發現佢好深黃值得投！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMdnqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMdnqU.png&h=a7f5cbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係：「自1994年起，工聯會林文輝已連續在龍上當選5屆區議員。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxjZhZt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxjZhZt.png&h=89a4d74b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工聯會出賣港人，以為唔洗還？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bN7eDOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbN7eDOF.jpg&h=47dc27d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30r3w8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30r3w8G.jpg&h=5ead3d31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c25cd2447d27d581e4bd3aa688940117b1605b","tid":1677824,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">11.2 維園</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybOQ1aD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybOQ1aD.jpg&h=e5110d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntWi93Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntWi93Z.jpg&h=4c73d9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCFoBJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCFoBJ0.jpg&h=a4ce886d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF00DXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l